<br>
Friday starts at 6:00pm PST hopefully ending 12:00pm PST<br>
<br>
Goal is to clear first island and second island, then camp out on the third island.<br>
<br>
Saturday starts at 11:00pm PST to whenever...<br>
- Primary goal is to clear out third island twice.<br>
- Depending on how things go, clear out fourth island or part of it.<br>
<br>
Sunday starts at 11:00pm PST to whenever<br>
- Clear out fourth island<br>
- Possibly go to the next island<br>
<br>
**** COSTS ****<br>
<br>
Next is costs. I need to bring this up, not to discourage you, but to tell you up front so your aware of what you will be getting into. Plan on it costing about 500pp per person to attend (or more if things don't go smoothly), and the break down of the cost is as follows:<br>
<br>
- 100pp for Plane of Air Stones (2 trips very possible).<br>
- 200 - 260pp (depending on charisma) to purchase keys (funds in excess are used for spell components).<br>
- 150pp for the slaughter on Azarack island to summon corpses.<br>
- Funds in excess from keys obtained used to purchase coffins to get people to next island.<br>
<br>
And of course if we fail in anyway, that will be lost money, or if you have to leave early. We won't fail, but I do need to address that possibility.<br>
<br>
1ST ISLAND - 300pp<br>
<br>
- Costs 50pp for stones to TP up.<br>
- After killing the creatures on this island, we obtain 24 key pieces to the next island. Therefore if we have 40 people 16 people have to purchase keys to get to the next island.<br>
<br>
2ND ISLAND - 200pp (maybe)<br>
<br>
- We have to fight 9 mobs, and depending on how quickly they notice us, will determine if we kill them all or not. We had 51 enchanters and they kept resisting mez, therefore we have to fight them all at once (unless higher level enchanter available). It isn't unlikely that we will lose the battle, so we will kill as many as we can, and have one monk play dead.<br>
- Therefore if we lose, that's when you go to the bank again and get another 200pp for stones and coffins to summon your corpse.<br>
- 20 to 24 key pieces drop.<br>
<br>
3RD ISLAND<br>
<br>
- Because we are short on keys (not 40 keys drop) we take the excess funds from above and purchase coffins. Then we duel on island two, revive on island two, summon corpse to island three, then revive on island three.<br>
<br>
Therefore if your planning on attending in the future, plan on high costs involved with this trip.<br>
<br>
Also, if your wondering a good place to get money, go to Sebillis, lots of nice gems drop there, you can make easily 100pp + per trip.<br>
<br>
OTHER OPTIONS: Depending on how many creatures was killed, we may not Teleport everyone back up, just enough to finish killing the rest of the creatures. Then we raise the bodies from there.<br>
<br>
***** TREASURE *****<br>
<br>
I never really figured out the best way to do loot for POA.  If we allow you to win only one item, not a whole lot of benefit from the trip, yet, if someone else is winning all the pieces tends not to be fair.<br>
<br>
So I think I do it this way, you can win one quest piece per island.<br>
<br>
You can win one item per trip (not quest piece, but some of the items you turn the quest pieces in for can drop).<br>
<br>
Please comment if you have any comments regarding treasure, so I can attempt to make it as fair as possible.<br>
<br>
<br>
***** ATTENDANCE *****<br>
<br>
We really need people that can show up all three days.  It's VERY expensive to bring new people in, in order to have enough people to do the plane.<br>
<br>
<br>
***** OTHER NOTES *****<br>
<br>
When we are short on key pieces we use coffins to get people to the next island.  This is accomplished by dueling, revive, summon corpse, revive.  Just so you know you will be dueling to get to other islands.<br>
<br>
Bind yourself in Halfling city, to prevent delays.<br>
<br>
